```
Checks if binary ends with 
``0x[FF AA AA]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes ends-with 0x[FF AA AA]
true

```
Checks if binary ends with 
``0x[11]``
.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 0x[1F FF AA AA] | bytes ends-with 0x[11]
false

```
